A complete changelog can be found at: https://github.com/Cashiuus/

~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2015-01-04
Version 1.5
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Converted GIT_BASE_DIR to a list and moved to settings.py.
    - Added ability to auto-scan your git folders and auto-update them.
      We'll ignore catching errors for now to avoid screwing up a repo.
    - Added debug functionality and text coloring


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2014-12-29
Version 1.4
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Built helper file "default.py" and migrated user-configured settings
    - Incorporated file/folder backup functionality with exclusions list
    - Improved Google Chrome installer/updater


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2014-03-20
Version 1.3
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Changed git repository settings to nested mappings
    - Added support for special git projects that require unique configurations


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2014-03-20
Version 1.2
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Added printout of current interpreter engine versions for reference


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2014-03-20
Version 1.1
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Changed git clones list to a dictionary with each Git URL as value
    - Added ability to setup new git clone when dict item doesn't exist
    - Added option to add "Kali Bleeding Edge" repo to sources.list file
    - Fixed "raw_input()" to work in both Python 2.x and 3.x


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Date    2014-03-20
Version 1.0
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
    - Drafted initial application
